data.description: Bring your offers! This is your chance to own a spacious 2,030 sq ft brick home on a large corner lot in a friendly and convenient neighborhood. 3 large bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, eat in kitchen, formal dining room. FULLY fenced yard, 2 car garage, screened in lanai, and a separate laundry and workshop space! Bonus family room with gas fireplace. Storage and closet space galore. New electrical panel in 2020. New roof and water softener installed 2016. Come make this beautiful property into your dream home!
